room_title: Escape room "Audrey's Addiction" by Seven Keys to Escape in Milwaukee
room_description:
76-year-old Audrey Cumberbatch resides at Saddlebrook Retirement Home. In the recent weeks, there have been several complaints about Audrey, as she has approached many Saddlebrook residents asking to borrow money. As an employee of the retirement home, you decide to explore Audrey's abode to see for yourself if there is any cause for concern.
Will your team uncover the truth about Audrey before she wakes up from her afternoon nap?
